---
// Features component
---

<section id="features" class="py-20 bg-base-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Our Robotics Programs</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-base-content/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Discover the exciting programs and opportunities that make Blast Robotics a leader in FIRST Robotics Competition.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Program 1 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title justify-center text-2xl mb-2">FIRST Robotics Competition</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/70">
            Compete in the ultimate sport for the mind with teams worldwide, building industrial-sized robots to compete in exciting challenges.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Program 2 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title justify-center text-2xl mb-2">STEM Education</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/70">
            Learn science, technology, engineering, and mathematics through hands-on projects and real-world problem solving.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Program 3 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title justify-center text-2xl mb-2">Leadership Development</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/70">
            Build leadership skills, teamwork abilities, and confidence through mentorship and collaborative projects.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Program 4 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-success/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title justify-center text-2xl mb-2">Mentorship Program</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/70">
            Learn from experienced engineers and industry professionals who guide students through technical challenges.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Program 5 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-warning/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-warning" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2-2v2m8 0H8m8 0v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H10a2 2 0 01-2-2V6m8 0H8m0 0H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m0 0h8m0 0h2a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m0 0V6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title justify-center text-2xl mb-2">Community Outreach</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/70">
            Share STEM knowledge with younger students and inspire the next generation of innovators.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Program 6 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto w-16 h-16 bg-info/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-info" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM9 14a6 6 0 00-6 6v1h12v-1a6 6 0 00-6-6zM21 12h-6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title justify-center text-2xl mb-2">Scholarships & Awards</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/70">
            Gain recognition and scholarship opportunities through competition achievements and team participation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
